ssings be upon him, came out to us. When he stood in his place of prayer, he remembered that he was in a state of ritual impurity (junub). The Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15926,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/09\/05\/angels-bless-remain-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":25822,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Angels bless those who wait for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe prayer of a man in congregation is twenty-five times better than prayer in his home or shop. When he performs ablution in a good manner and leaves to the mosque only to perform the prayer,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41207,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/missing-salat-al-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":25822,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Warning against missing congregational \u2018Asr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever misses the afternoon prayer, it is as if he had lost his family and his property.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 552, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 626 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (aut